name: cred-rea-fish-team-belt-transect-survey-at-santa-rosa-bank-marianas-archipelago-2005
notes: Belt transects along 3 consecutively-placed, 25m transect lines were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 2 sites at Santa Rosa Bank in the Marianas Archipelago (MA) during 3 - 9 October 2005 in the NOAA Oscar Elton Sette (OES0512) Reef Assessment and Monitoring Program (RAMP) Cruise. Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
